{"type": "article", "id": 37492, "title": "Tiffany 的CEO突然离职，以及，David Bowie 回顾展不要错过 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-02-06T03:00:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 21691, "name": "DAVID BOWIE"}, {"id": 33975, "name": "Anti Social Social Club"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 8113, "name": "Ferragamo"}, {"id": 18765, "name": "藤原浩"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/201702061037111gUvDxLOo2KA0lwQ.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/salvatore-ferragamo-quashes-sale-rumors-plots-faster-growth-10776885/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ferragamo 公布 2016 财报，否认出售传言</b></a> | 上周五，Ferragamo 召开投资者会议，公布 2016 年财报，并且否认了近期关于该品牌将被出售的传言。财报显示，去年 Ferragamo 增速放缓至 1%，销售总额为 14.4 亿欧元。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/anthonydemarco/2017/02/05/frederic-cumenal-steps-down-as-tiffany-ceo/#48504435419f\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tiffany 的 CEO 离职，该决定当日生效</b></a> | 周日，Tiffany&amp;Co 集团宣布，它的 CEO Frederic Cumenal 离职，并且这项决定在当日生效。据 Tiffany&amp;Co 称，公司的董事会主席 Michael J. Kowalski 将担任临时 CEO，董事会将与猎头公司协调寻找下一个继任者。在一份声明中，该公司表示， Cumenal 离职的决定是基于令人失望的财务业绩。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/vans-japan-2017-spring-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 日本发布 2017 春季系列 lookbook</a>。其中，Vans 再度与中野史郎的 Rollicking 合作打造的传统横须贺纹样的 Slip-On 亮眼。这双鞋以黑色为主调，鞋面是龙与虎的图案，定价为 9000 日元，将于 3 月发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095113j2uGlFEzN5nacBTp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095135dZIFmwbLBga23zHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702060951358gbTznodj6hLyV1x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095136C6RNxvQHsJr2tgE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095136NKUJrftomFG1nv5g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095136aeAovO2xuXnlMNji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095137m0YyoFiT2khp6HKt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095138EtFpezmPCN4xb25H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095138ySc0qohg9VxP2wKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095138DpG2LhzsJ6XOEVvU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095150U5CRBvLlJDSNK4a1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/gucci-neo-vintage-luggage-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 推出全新复古行李袋款系列</a>。该系列包括「Soft GG Supreme duffle bag with Web」及「Soft GG Supreme tote」两个袋款。均采用了 GG Supreme 的独特材质打造，包袋正面的印花中则加入金色 logo 及骷髅头图案。而「Soft GG Supreme duffle bag with Web」的皮革制手抽有一只啡色和一只黄色更显特别。这两款包袋现已于美国上架，定价分别为 2450 美元及 1350 美元。&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095210QGaqRX2oJ7lVytBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095225E4tIUuao0K9xWr32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095226vc5Ftja3RTz67ieA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095227fdkGtrx5lDMYcgBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095238uMzX7Yd8Ur96TLna.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702060952480VibOu2kwpe8IJNt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095250cNYlAiP7ZDHVgnse.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>街头潮牌 Anti Social Social Club 与 Modernica 合作，推出联名款玻璃纤维贝壳椅。这把椅子由 Charles 和 Ray Eames 设计，在 2000 年再度复活，是以玻璃纤维手工打造的知名设计师椅子。在去年，也曾与 Undefeated 联名推出 100 把限量椅。在这次与 Anti Social Social Club 的合作中，签名式粉红配色加上经典品牌字体 Logo，非常抢眼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095305i31YyhJTGXVaFCPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在东京银座的索尼大楼拆除之际，开设在索尼大楼的地下停车库之中的藤原浩概念店舖  THE PARK · ING GINZA，再一次推出了索尼特别系列。该系列除了印有「Walkman」和「It’s a Sony」等字样的 T-Shirt、帽衫、Coach Jacket 和 Tote Bag 之外，以历代 walkman 播放器为原型的小袋设计成为了最大亮点。该系列将于 2 月 10 日起在 THE PARK · ING GINZA 正式发售，定价从 &nbsp;3000 到 16000 日元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095322Jsu4e0fgMrcWpULh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095323nMtpxcw8RZ2ISs7f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095323jx0iuGq7sMlVbENS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702060953232sxKjUg6Ny3lkvLz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667024\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017020609532329yU5NnbSPg4refJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667355\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095323uKwWRl85J7TxrNBD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667722\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702060953231Krg3dz7vSoRBUyp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095323b9SZVnU3Ec4kI2AL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095323LYADdlK4kanI1i76.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667028\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095324qKzrxWwg6joVH9Zv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665948\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095324B5Y0mN8ctwP7u2ZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667042\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095324GEYUuy0sKMbirCc1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667436\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095332FMoLzEj0Dwp82yiN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665934\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095332f78OR4mu0MFYc3jS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/david-bowie-is\" rel=\"nofollow\">亚洲唯一一场 David Bowie 生涯回顾展《DAVID BOWIE is</a>》，已于 1 月 8 日，David Bowie 70 岁冥诞当日在天王洲寺田仓库盛大开展。这次展览由伦敦 V &amp; A 博物馆策展，精选了 300 多件展品，内容横跨 David Bowie 不同年代的舞台表演服装、歌词手稿与各类型珍贵影像。日本场更展出特别限定展「David Bowie Meets Japan」，还邀请了曾与 David Bowie 共演名作《Merry Christmas, Mr. Lawrence》的导演北野武与音乐大师坂本龙一。<br></p><p class=\"\">展览位于东京都品川区东品川 2-6-10 的寺田仓库，截止至 2017 年 4 月 9 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095344usxo5BOWScT9AEfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095345gF5A9mYhGr8ykx4v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095411netQGsRPzrZl9w1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206095412BFhw694IPz5oJMSm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206100101PuV2Jmq78ZixMDFk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677493\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170206100113Z5wWz8hbBOgjyGX6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/david-bowie-is\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}